               <metamark function="insert">^</metamark>
            </add>
            <add place="superlinear" xml:id="c56-0024__main__d5e4690">you</add>
         </mod> have <seg xml:id="C08_app835-fMS">
            <lb n="c56-0025__main__1"/>"so</seg> greedily  <seg xml:id="C08_app837-fMS">imbibed</seg> are  <seg xml:id="C08_app839-fMS">
            <del rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0025__main__d5e4704">at le</del> a</seg>
         <seg xml:id="C08_app840-fMS">
            <lb n="c56-0025__main__2"/>"thousand</seg> years  <seg xml:id="C08_app842-fMS">old</seg> and as musty as  <seg xml:id="C08_app844-fMS">
            <lb n="c56-0025__main__3"/>" <del rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0025__main__d5e4711">your</del> they are</seg>
         <seg xml:id="C08_app845-fMS">ancient.</seg> I little  <seg xml:id="C08_app847-fMS">expected</seg>
         <seg xml:id="C08_app848-fMS">
            <lb n="c56-0025__main__4"/>"in</seg> this enlightened and scientific  <seg xml:id="C08_app850-fMS">age</seg>
         <seg xml:id="C08_app851-fMS">
            <lb n="c56-0025__main__5"/>"to</seg> find a disciple of Albertus  <seg xml:id="C08_app853-fMS">
            <w ana="start"/>Mag<lb n="c56-0025__main__6"/>"nus<w ana="end"/>
         </seg> and Paracelsus. My dear  <seg xml:id="C08_app855-fMS">sir <lb n="c56-0025__main__7"/>"you</seg> must begin your studies <w ana="start"/>entire<lb n="c56-0025__main__8"/>ly<w ana="end"/> anew." So <seg xml:id="C08_app859-fMS">saying</seg> he  <seg xml:id="C08_app861-fMS">ste <mod xml:id="c56-0025__main__d5e4734">
               <mdel>ss</mdel>
               <add hand="#pbs" place="intralinear" xml:id="c56-0025__main__d5e4738">pp </add>
            </mod> ed</seg> aside, and  <seg xml:id="C08_app863-fMS">
            <lb n="c56-0025__main__9"/>
            <del rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0025__main__d5e4744">wh</del> wrote down a list of several <lb n="c56-0025__main__10"/>books</seg>
         <seg xml:id="C08_app864-fMS">
            <del rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0025__main__d5e4750">
               <unclear>u</unclear>
            </del> upon</seg> natural  <seg xml:id="C08_app866-fMS">philosophy</seg>
         <lb n="c56-0025__main__11"/>which he desired me to <seg xml:id="C08_app868-fMS">procure</seg>
         <lb n="c56-0025__main__12"/>and dismissed <seg xml:id="C08_app870-fMS">me</seg> after mentioning <lb n="c56-0025__main__13"/>that <seg xml:id="C08_app872-fMS">
            <del rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0025__main__d5e4761">he intended</del>
            <del rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0025__main__d5e4765">to commen</del> in <lb n="c56-0025__main__14"/>the beginning of the</seg>
         <seg xml:id="C08_app873-fMS">next</seg> week <lb n="c56-0025__main__15"/>he intended to commence a course <lb n="c56-0025__main__16"/>of lectures upon natural philosophy <seg part="I" xml:id="C08_app875-fMS__I">
            </seg>
