            </mod>
            <del rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0026__main__d5e4885">But when the ne</del>
            <w ana="start"/>Be<lb n="c56-0026__main__2"/>sides<w ana="end"/>
         </seg> I had a contempt for the uses <lb n="c56-0026__main__3"/>of modern <seg part="I" xml:id="C08_app909-fMS__I">
