            </add>
         </mod>
         <seg part="F" xml:id="C08_app910-fMS__F"> .</seg> It was very  <seg xml:id="C08_app912-fMS">
            <lb n="c56-0026__main__4"/>
            <del rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0026__main__d5e4908">when</del> different</seg> when the  <seg xml:id="C08_app914-fMS">
