            <lb n="c56-0026__main__9"/>of chimera overthrew at</seg> the  <seg xml:id="C08_app927-fMS">same <lb n="c56-0026__main__10"/>time all <mod xml:id="c56-0026__main__d5e4953">
               <del rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0026__main__d5e4955">greatness in the science</del>
