            <anchor xml:id="c56-0026.01"/>
            <lb n="c56-0026__left_margin__1"/>the <del rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0026__left_margin__d5e4976">utmost</del>
            <lb n="c56-0026__left_margin__2"/>ambition of <lb n="c56-0026__left_margin__3"/>enquirer</seg> seemed <lb n="c56-0026__left_margin__4"/>to limit itself <lb n="c56-0026__left_margin__5"/>to the <w ana="start"/>annihi<lb n="c56-0026__left_margin__6"/>lation<w ana="end"/> of those <lb n="c56-0026__left_margin__7"/>visions on which <anchor xml:id="c56-0026.02"/>
         <anchor xml:id="c56-0026.04"/>
         <lb n="c56-0026__left_margin__1"/>my interest in science <lb n="c56-0026__left_margin__2"/>was chiefly founded. <lb n="c56-0026__left_margin__3"/>I was required <lb n="c56-0026__left_margin__4"/>to exchange <lb n="c56-0026__left_margin__5"/>chimeras of <lb n="c56-0026__left_margin__6"/>boundless <seg xml:id="C08_app929-fMS">grandeur,</seg>
