            <lb n="c56-0026__main__14"/>commenced</seg> I thought of the <w ana="start"/>infor<lb n="c56-0026__main__15"/>mation<w ana="end"/>
         <seg xml:id="C08_app939-fMS">M <shi rend="sup">r</shi> . K. <mod xml:id="c56-0026__main__d5e5086">
               <mdel>—</mdel>
               <add place="superlinear" xml:id="c56-0026__main__d5e5090">rempe </add>
            </mod>
         </seg> had given me <lb n="c56-0026__main__16"/>concerning the <seg xml:id="C08_app941-fMS">lectures,</seg> and although <lb n="c56-0026__main__17"/>I could not consent to go and hear <lb n="c56-0026__main__18"/>that little conceited fellow deliver <lb n="c56-0026__main__19"/>sentences <seg xml:id="C08_app943-fMS">
