               </add>
               <add place="superlinear" xml:id="c56-0026__main__d5e5111">out of a pulpit</add>
            </mod>
         </seg> I recollected what he had <lb n="c56-0026__main__20"/>said of <seg xml:id="C08_app945-fMS">M <shi rend="sup">r</shi> . Waldham,</seg> whom I had <lb n="c56-0026__main__21"/>never <seg xml:id="C08_app947-fMS">seen <del rend="strikethrough" xml:id="c56-0026__main__d5e5122">and</del>
         </seg> as he had  <seg xml:id="C08_app949-fMS">been <lb n="c56-0026__main__22"/>hitherto</seg> out of town. <milestone unit="tei:p-END"/>
