         <seg part="F" xml:id="C08_app952-fMS__F">curiosity</seg> and partly from  <seg xml:id="C08_app954-fMS">
            <lb n="c56-0026__main__24"/>idleness</seg> I went into the lecturing  <seg xml:id="C08_app956-fMS">room</seg>
